tion catches the realistic malformed inputs (wrong mode, missing token, empty token, whitespace-only token, wrong types). The NUL-only dict token gap (W1) is a low-probability edge that should be closed in a follow-up hardening pass but does not block merge. Rating: **4/5**, no blockers.",
